<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Welcome to Recipes App</h1>

  <h2>Overview</h2>

  <p>
    Recipes App is a user-friendly web application designed to make your
    culinary journey delightful. With a diverse set of features, it caters to
    both seasoned cooks and beginners. Explore user-submitted recipes, create
    your own culinary masterpieces, get random recipe suggestions, and
    effortlessly manage your grocery list.
  </p>

  <h2>Features</h2>

  <h4>1. Browse Recipes</h4>

  <p>
    Discover a collection of user-submitted recipes from various cuisines. The
    "Recipes" tab allows you to explore different dishes and find inspiration
    for your next meal.
  </p>

  <h4>2. Create New Recipes</h4>

  <p>
    Share your favorites! The "New Recipe" tab provides a simple and intuitive
    interface for users to share their favorite recipes with the community. Add
    ingredients and instructions for all to see.
  </p>

  <h4>3. Get Random Recipe Suggestions</h4>

  <p>
    Indecisive? Use the "Suggestions" tab to get an idea for a new recipe you
    can create. Whether you're looking for a quick snack or a gourmet dinner,
    let us surprise you with diverse and delicious options based on the weather
    conditions in your area.
  </p>

  <h4>4. Manage Grocery List</h4>

  <p>
    Effortlessly plan your shopping with the "Grocery List" functionality. Add
    existing recipes to your grocery list, making it easy to gather all the
    ingredients you need for your chosen recipes.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Use</h2>

  <h4>1. Browse Recipes</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>Navigate to the "Recipes" tab.</li>
    <li>
      Click on a recipe to view details, including ingredients and instructions.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h4>2. Create New Recipes</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>Go to the "New Recipe" tab.</li>
    <li>
      Fill out the required fields, such as title, ingredients, and
      instructions.
    </li>
    <li>Submit your recipe to share it with the community.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>3. Get Random Recipe Suggestions</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>Visit the "Suggestions" tab.</li>
    <li>Submit a temperature to receive a random recipe recommendation.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>4. Manage Grocery List</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>Access the "Grocery List" tab.</li>
    <li>
      Browse and select existing recipes to add their ingredients to your
      grocery list.
    </li>
    <li>Review and update your grocery list as needed.</li>
    <li>Use the list for convenient shopping.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
